{"id": 2598, "title": "Ticket #2598: Allow job_queue.log to be in a different directory than SPOOL", "description": "<blockquote>\nCurrently, the file job_queue.log must reside in the $(SPOOL) directory.  The schedd frequently fsync's the job_queue.log, which can be very expensive.  We'd like to put the job_queue.log on an SSD, but can't fit rest of spool there.  So, we'd like a new knob to control just where the job-queue.log goes.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Nov-01 12:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/11c778486c8cee611243f0c71cdacdfd1fe8e3c0\">[28077]</a></span>: complete documentation of new knob: JOB_QUEUE_LOG ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2598\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2598'); return false;\" title=\"Allow job_queue.log to be in a different directory than SPOOL\">#2598</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-Oct-31 12:47</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/26fc2b753c618c26d1955d89e334288a657dc12e\">[28062]</a></span>: Document JOB_QUEUE_LOG knob <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2598\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2598'); return false;\" title=\"Allow job_queue.log to be in a different directory than SPOOL\">#2598</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></